                    THE UNIVERSITY OF NEBRASKA
                    UNIVERSITY OF NEBRASKA PRESS
                    LINCOLN 8, NEBRASKA
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="postmark">
                    LINCOLN REB 21'61 NEBR P.B. METER 358475 U.S. POSTAGE 04
                </ab>
                
                <ab type="address">
                    John Neihardt Skyrim, Route 7
                    Columbia, Missouri
                </ab>
                
            </div1>
            
